description: This Chainlink VRF common Cooter purrs with a rating of 16, and a multiplier of 1x. It has a total score of 16, and confers the same amount of votes in the EtherCats DAO. The card game properties are Nine Lives for North, Stringalong for East, Leverage for South, and 3 for West. Cooter has the personality suit of punter. Each Founders Series cat is part of NFT history. These fine felines represent the first verifiably random packs minted with Chainlink VRF.
name: Cooter [16 Votes, Common]
